quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  13,43,"Ne abakhayi baboolanga mbu shiwarumwa tawe. Boola mbu; “Nyasaye ayela okhuba omuloli hakari wanje ninanyu, nende ulia uli nende obumanyi bweshitabu.""
  14,1,"Alif Lam Ra. Eshitabu shiakhweshia khwiwe kho orusie Abandu mufiilima obayile mubulafu, khubuchami bwa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, oboosie khunjila ya ulia Owamani, Owitsomibungwa muno."
  14,2,"Nyasaye, ulia owebili mwikulu nende khushialo bioosi nebibie yenyene. Ne eshinyasio eshilulu shiliba khubakhayi."
  14,3,"Balia bachamanga obulamu bwokhushialo okhushila bwomwikulu, ne bekalilanga injila ya Nyasaye, ne bayienyelanga okhwikotiombokha. Abo bali mubukori obwa hale."
  14,4,"Ne shikhwaruma Omurumwa yesiyesi tawe, halali khulusungo olwa abandu baye, kho anyoole okhubenoosilia; mana Nyasaye akosinjia owayenya, ne alunjisia owayenya. Naye niye wa Amaani, Owamachesi."
  14,5,"Ne toto khwaruma Musa nende ebimanyisio biefu (nikhumuboolela mbu); “Rusia abandu bo okhurula mufiilima okhutsia mubulafu, ne obetsulisie tsinyanga tsia Nyasaye.” Toto mu ako khulimwo nende ebifune khubalia befwilanga, nende okhupa orio muno."